<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Z1 Governance — Governed AI. Actually.</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <style>
    *, ::before, ::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; border: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg:        #0A0E12;
      --bg-2:      #0D1117;
      --bg-3:      #1A1F26;
      --bg-4:      #121719;
      --surface:   #1A1F26;
      --border:    #232A33;
      --border-2:  #3A434F;
      --green:     #19F9A6;
      --green-dim: rgba(25,249,166,0.06);
      --green-glow:rgba(25,249,166,0.25);
      --red:       #E63946;
      --red-dim:   rgba(230,57,70,0.08);
      --blue:      #38BDF8;
      --text:      #E6EDF3;
      --text-2:    #9FB0C0;
      --text-3:    #6E7F8E;
      --mono:      'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      --sans:      'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--sans); line-height: 1.5; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button { cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; background: transparent; border: none; }
    img, video { display: block; max-width: 100%; }

    /* NAV */
    .nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 30;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(10,14,18,0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 72rem; margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .nav-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      width: 2.25rem; height: 2.25rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      color: var(--green); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700;
      background: var(--green-dim);
    }
    .nav-brand-text p:first-child { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--text); }
    .nav-brand-text p:last-child  { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-3); }
    .nav-links { display: none; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; }
    .nav-links a, .nav-links button {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-2); transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links button:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-cta {
      border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem; color: var(--green) !important;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .nav-links { display: flex; } }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      position: relative; min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden; padding: 7rem 1.5rem; text-align: left;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .hero { text-align: center; } }
    .hero-video {
      position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    }
    .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(10,14,18,0.78); }
    .hero-content { position: relative; max-width: 48rem; }
    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.35em; color: var(--blue);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(2.5rem,8vw,6rem);
      font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: var(--text);
      text-shadow: rgba(25,249,166,0.08) 0 0 22px;
    }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--green); text-shadow: var(--green-glow) 0 0 18px; }
    .hero-oneliner {
      margin-top: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.875rem); line-height: 2.25rem; color: var(--text);
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.875rem); line-height: 2.25rem; color: var(--text-2);
    }
    .hero-subtitle span { color: var(--green); text-shadow: var(--green-glow) 0 0 12px; }
    .hero-tagline {
      margin-top: 0.75rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--blue);
    }
    .hero-body {
      margin-top: 1.75rem; max-width: 42rem;
      font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.75rem; color: var(--text-2);
    }
    .hero-body .allow { color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-body .block { color: var(--red);   font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-ctas {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .hero-ctas { flex-direction: row; } }
    .btn-primary {
      width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--bg); background: var(--green);
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .btn-primary { width: auto; } }
    .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%; border: 1px solid var(--blue); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--blue); background: rgba(56,189,248,0.08);
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .btn-secondary { width: auto; } }
    .hero-saas {
      margin-top: 1.25rem; max-width: 42rem;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-3);
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    .section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    .section-inner { max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-inner-wide { max-width: 64rem; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-inner-center { max-width: 64rem; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .section-alt { background: var(--bg-2); }

    .section-title {
      margin-top: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(1.875rem,4vw,2.25rem); font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.25; color: var(--text);
    }
    .section-body { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75rem; color: var(--text-2); }

    /* ARCHITECTURE */
    .arch-intro {
      margin-top: 1.25rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(1.125rem,2.5vw,1.5rem); line-height: 2rem; color: var(--text);
    }
    .arch-closer {
      margin-top: 2rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.875rem); font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: var(--text);
    }
    .arch-closer span { color: var(--green); }

    /* EXECUTION */
    .exec-slogan {
      margin-top: 2.5rem; display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(1.125rem,2.5vw,1.5rem);
      font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--green);
      background: var(--green-dim);
    }
    .exec-ctas { margin-top: 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .exec-ctas { flex-direction: row; } }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 0.875rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; }

    /* SIMULATOR */
    .simulator-shell {
      margin-top: 2rem; overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 0.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      background: #12171D;
    }
    .simulator-titlebar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #1A1F26;
    }
    .sim-dots { display: flex; gap: 0.375rem; }
    .sim-dot { width: 0.625rem; height: 0.625rem; border-radius: 9999px; background: #2A3540; }
    .sim-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--text-3); }
    .sim-live { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; }
    .sim-live-dot { width: 0.375rem; height: 0.375rem; border-radius: 9999px; background: var(--green); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--green); }
    .sim-live span { color: var(--green); }
    .simulator-body { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .sim-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .sim-form { flex-direction: row; } }
    .sim-input {
      flex: 1; border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text); background: var(--bg); outline: none;
    }
    .sim-input:focus { border-color: var(--green); }
    .sim-submit {
      flex-shrink: 0; border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--bg); background: var(--green);
    }
    .sim-chips { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .sim-chip {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 9999px;
      padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-2); cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .sim-chip:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
    .sim-result { margin-top: 1rem; display: none; }
    .sim-result.visible { display: block; }
    .verdict-allow { color: var(--green); font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700; }
    .verdict-block { color: var(--red);   font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700; }
    .verdict-stop  { color: var(--blue);  font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700; }
    .sim-result-box {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.6;
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    /* LEDGER */
    .ledger-tally {
      margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline;
      justify-content: space-between; gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .ledger-counts {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.25rem); font-weight: 700;
    }
    .ledger-allowed { color: var(--green); }
    .ledger-sep { color: var(--text-3); }
    .ledger-blocked { color: var(--red); }
    .ledger-clear-btn {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-3);
      text-underline-offset: 4px;
    }
    .ledger-clear-btn:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .ledger-table {
      margin-top: 2rem; overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }
    .ledger-head {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 2fr 0.9fr 1fr;
      gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.625rem; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--text-3);
      background: #1A1F26;
    }
    .ledger-rows { max-height: 420px; overflow-y: auto; }
    .ledger-row {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 2fr 0.9fr 1fr;
      gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem;
    }
    .ledger-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .ledger-ts { color: var(--text-3); overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
    .ledger-cmd { color: var(--text); overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
    .verdict-badge {
      display: inline-block; border-radius: 0.25rem;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.6875rem;
    }
    .badge-allow { color: var(--green); border: 1px solid var(--green); background: rgba(25,249,166,0.08); }
    .badge-block { color: var(--red);   border: 1px solid var(--red);   background: var(--red-dim); }
    .badge-stop  { color: var(--blue);  border: 1px solid var(--blue);  background: rgba(56,189,248,0.08); }
    .ledger-seal-allow { color: var(--green); overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
    .ledger-seal-block { color: var(--red);   overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
    .ledger-note { margin-top: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-3); }

    /* SEAL GRID */
    .seal-grid {
      margin-top: 3rem; display: grid; gap: 1px;
      overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--border);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .seal-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    .seal-card { padding: 2rem; background: #1A1F26; }
    .seal-card-title {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--green);
    }
    .seal-card-body { margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75rem; color: var(--text-2); }

    /* FOOTER / PILOT */
    .footer { border-top: 2px solid var(--border); padding: 6rem 1.5rem; background: var(--bg); }
    .footer-inner { max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .footer-inner { text-align: center; } }
    .pilot-title {
      margin-top: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem); font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text);
    }
    .pilot-subtitle {
      margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(1.125rem,2.5vw,1.5rem);
      line-height: 2rem; color: var(--text-2);
    }
    .pilot-oneliner { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75rem; color: var(--text); }
    .pilot-couplet { margin-top: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75rem; color: var(--text-2); }
    .pilot-couplet span { color: var(--green); }
    .pilot-product-tag { margin-top: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5rem; color: var(--blue); }
    .pilot-saas { margin-top: 1.25rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-3); }
    .pilot-hmac { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-2); }
    .pilot-hmac-badge {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--green);
      background: var(--green-dim);
    }

    /* PRICING */
    .pricing-band {
      margin-top: 2.5rem; max-width: 42rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
      background: rgba(25,249,166,0.03);
    }
    .pricing-label {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--green);
    }
    .pricing-row {
      margin-top: 0.75rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center; gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .price-block { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .price-big { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: clamp(1.875rem,4vw,2.25rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .price-unit { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-3); }
    .price-save { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--blue); }
    .pricing-partner { margin-top: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--blue); }
    .pricing-terms { margin-top: 0.75rem; max-width: 36rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-2); }

    .pilot-ctas {
      margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .pilot-ctas { flex-direction: row; } }
    .pilot-email { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--blue); }
    .pilot-qualifier { margin-top: 0.75rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-2); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }

    /* FOOTER WORDMARK */
    .footer-wordmark {
      margin-top: 3.5rem; padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .footer-wordmark { flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; } }
    .footer-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .footer-logo {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      width: 2rem; height: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 0.375rem;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--green); background: var(--green-dim);
    }
    .footer-brand-name { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--text); }
    .footer-tagline { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.6875rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--text-3); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<header class="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#hero" class="nav-brand">
      <div class="nav-logo">Z1</div>
      <div class="nav-brand-text">
        <p>Z1 Governance</p>
        <p>Governed AI. Actually.</p>
      </div>
    </a>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="#execution">Execution</a>
      <a href="#simulator">Simulator</a>
      <a href="#ledger">Ledger</a>
      <a href="#seal">The seal</a>
      <a href="#pilot">Pilot</a>
      <a href="#pilot" class="nav-cta">Discuss a pilot</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <video class="hero-video" src="https://storage.googleapis.com/audos-images/workspace-media/38f62d24-1a54-4975-8bbc-22574b3d16c9/1781359371711_3lh9o6hh.mp4" autoplay loop playsinline muted></video>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="eyebrow">Deterministic governance &amp; audit layer</p>
    <h1>Governed AI. <span>Actually.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-oneliner">Z1 holds your business.</p>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">The model proposes. <span>Python disposes.</span></p>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Knows you instead of just remembering you.</p>
    <p class="hero-body">
      Z1 is a deterministic governance and audit layer that sits under your AI agents.
      Every action an agent proposes runs through a gate that returns a verdict —
      <span class="allow">ALLOW</span> or <span class="block">BLOCK</span> —
      with the evidence behind it, and a receipt you can read.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="#pilot" class="btn-primary">Request a Pilot</a>
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('simulator').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Try the Gate</button>
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('ledger').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Verify the Ledger</button>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-saas">Each client gets a live, governed environment at z1governs.com/clientname — a configured microsite at your own URL. No zip files. No IT calls.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ARCHITECTURE -->
<section id="architecture" class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">In plain terms</p>
    <p class="arch-intro">
      Z1 sits between your AI and your computer. Before the AI is allowed to do anything —
      send a file, run a command, touch your data — Z1 checks it against your rules and
      writes down the decision. The AI suggests. Z1 decides. And every decision leaves a
      receipt you can read.
    </p>
    <p class="section-body">
      Model-level compliance is best-effort — a model complies until it doesn't.
      Z1 does not ask the model to behave. It checks the action in deterministic Python
      before the action can happen.
    </p>
